<H3> <TI>     High-Temperature Engineering Test Reactor Under Construction </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  946C0002B Tokyo GENSHIRYOKU KOGYO in Japanese Aug 93 pp 
16-25 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 946C0002B </F>
<F P=104>  Tokyo GENSHIRYOKU KOGYO </F>
