<H3> <TI>     Durability of Nuclear Power Plant Materials </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  946C0002C Tokyo GENSHIRYOKU KOGYO in Japanese Aug 93 pp 
26-35 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 946C0002C </F>
<F P=104>  Tokyo GENSHIRYOKU KOGYO </F>
